name: UFO In Outer Space
description:
UFO In Outer Space is an arcade game where you have to help the UFO escape the BLACK HOLE. In addition to the black hole istelf, the white borders will also kill you. Therefore you should collect as many items as possible to not get squished!

The game is made by me. My Discord: Eirik#6524

Controls:

The only movement control you have is jumping/flapping.

Keyboard: Spacebar or W

Controller: Dualshock Cross, Xbox A, Nintendo B
